This Repeater is a member of the Salop Cluster TG75 on Slot 1,
Please refrain from Using Slot 1 for other than TG75 (23575)
Slot 2 can be used for local call eg TT on this site only on TG9 or TG235251
Best is to use 235251 for normal use of this Repeater then others can join you from others sites by using 235251 to contact there end to this repeater.
e.g. if you use TG25173 GB7EH this will connect GB7EH to GB7BM on this TG.
Please contact the keeper via https://www.facebook.com
